OL,3,CHeat drives tortoises to escape owners
OL,4,Cin search of love
OL,6,FOwners are being encouraged to check
OL,7,Fon their tortoises as the record heat
OL,8,Fin Guernsey has led to some escaping
OL,9,Fin search of a partner.
OL,11,FThe GSPCA says that three were picked
OL,12,Fup across the island throughout the
OL,13,Fweek, with the Bailiwick experiencing
OL,14,Fits hottest-ever day on Thursday as
OL,15,Ftemperatures surpassed 36C.
OL,17,FThe trio are being looked after by the
OL,18,Fcharity and were found close to each
OL,19,Fother on Epinelle Road, Oatlands Lane,
OL,20,Fand Capelles Road in St Sampson.
OL,26,@wD@ZOX
