OL,3,CHeat drives tortoises to escape owners
OL,4,Cin search of love
OL,6,FThe animal shelter's manager, Steve
OL,7,FByrne, told ITV News: "Every summer,
OL,8,Fwe see a number of stray tortoises.
OL,10,F"On these extreme sunny days, they get
OL,11,Fvery, very lively and quite excitable."
OL,13,FMale tortoises are much more likely to
OL,14,Fflee their owners and are usually in
OL,15,Fsearch of a mating partner, according
OL,16,Fto Steve.
OL,18,FHe went on to warn that people "might
OL,19,Fnot be aware of just how good the
OL,20,Fanimals are at climbing and digging
OL,21,Funderneath fences".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
