OL,3,CHeat drives tortoises to escape owners
OL,4,Cin search of love
OL,6,FAnyone who is missing an animal can
OL,7,Fcall the GSPCA on 01481 257261 - while
OL,8,Fthey are also appealing for sightings
OL,9,Fof 'Hippo', a tortoise that has
OL,10,Fdisappeared from Rue Feveresse in St
OL,11,FSaviour.
OL,13,FThankfully for owners, while the
OL,14,FChannel Islands are facing their
OL,15,Fsecond heatwave in a matter of weeks,
OL,16,Ftemperatures are expected to cool in
OL,17,Fthe coming days.
